{"tid":693990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔使用手擔遮喇 日本AI結合無人機服侍你","createTime":"2018-06-08T02:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T02:55:51.000Z","uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a57ce818392418c22aafd5b36bb5a310b04f7764","tid":693990,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180608&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58280704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180608%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58280704&d=7i8o4Sq34BBSIKgKlxru8i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e89f83dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180608%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58280704&h=c5800309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180608&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58280704</a><br />\n<br />\n【科技●國際專欄】唔使用手擔遮喇 日本AI結合無人機服侍你<br />\n<br />\n相傳中國春秋戰國時代已有人發明出雨傘，經過二千多年，除了材質和細微結構外，雨傘的外形和用法基本上也沒有進步過，人類總是要重覆「落雨擔遮」，問題是人類雙手越來越忙，又要打字又要影相又要俾like，如果一隻手要擔遮，你叫我點樣單手「食雞」？<br />\n<br />\n人工智能幫到你。不是以後由AI幫你打機覆message，是由AI幫你擔遮。<br />\n<br />\n日本栃木縣一間IT公司，正致力開發人工智能擔遮系統「free Parasol」；遮，仍然是一把遮，但就與四部無人機結合，變成一把「飛遮」，可持續飛行一個小時，最重要是，遮頂附有人工智能感應器，能夠控制無人機追蹤使用者，只要按按遮柄上的掣，無人機便會啟動開遮升空，沿途全自動幫你擋雨遮太陽。<br />\n<br />\n該公司負責人表示，希望「飛遮」能為雨傘巿場帶來改革，並主要為殘障人士帶來方便，但公司仍要解決不少技術問題，例如氣流的影響，不然「飛遮」分分鐘變成「AI血滴子」。<br />\n<br />\n「飛遮」預計在2019年中發售，售價約在3萬日圓左右，2000港紙買把遮貴唔貴？"},{"pid":"e6e6c986e1b734724c28c56607227ff7dd8b2b0a","tid":693990,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/104859_d95bc7bbdd588e3bb1e8daa615a92d5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F104859_d95bc7bbdd588e3bb1e8daa615a92d5b.png&h=67149857&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/104939_1fd2d779857909e247afd0e5682c9929.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F104939_1fd2d779857909e247afd0e5682c9929.png&h=7f7ba332&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36da0843423501f6f9592f33bf0ab50e59c61228","tid":693990,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"師奶血滴子  VS  AI血滴子"},{"pid":"d258401201b2d0f1990cfd79c8078a7bab1aa1a8","tid":693990,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"剃頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beae982250c22c14dc3bf8d7754ba5c8a2c59d48","tid":693990,"uid":36452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:51:55.000Z","msg":"買呢把遮係香港既行人路用, 係咪要定保險先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aa8144a3f52e448af835d2090c6549b264a538","tid":693990,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:53:40.000Z","msg":"其他人唔敢埋身，可以霸唒條路嚟行"},{"pid":"54688235465fc01e6dcb6a40f754d37280078ea8","tid":693990,"uid":134226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"見到AI 日本 服侍<br />\n以為係飛機杯無人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}